{"tid":401064,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成日覺得，人生你衰邊瓣都得，as long as你唔生仔","createTime":"2017-09-15T10:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T04:43:15.000Z","uid":58316,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73249869b0adec211774ad1ac79f4be9432687d1","tid":401064,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:20:58.000Z","msg":"失學，大不了報過第間，通街學店，一係出來揾食<br />\n失業，抖下先囉，騎牛揾馬，冇老婆仔女等你開飯，唔駛養家進修下又得<br />\n投資失利，assume用自己錢，咪再儲過囉，好似打機咁重玩<br />\n負資產，破產囉，搬返屋企同老豆老母住<br />\n但你生仔，真係噩夢既開端，叫天不應，叫地不聞<br />\n如果你人生曾經低潮過，可以同你講，生細路後人生可以比你人生任何低潮痛苦千百倍<br />\n好似俾個籠困住，伸手不見五指，想嗌救命但又嗌唔出聲好似啞左咁，想喊又喊唔出眼淚，只往心裏流"},{"pid":"3c74c64523b9fbcb907bce5f943fda30ee09f9af","tid":401064,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"agger, 最怕有包伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fdf88636431a01532c346382023e1f64520c780","tid":401064,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:34:49.000Z","msg":"為什麼要製造生老病死?"},{"pid":"03f45cc98121e86414f64951253e3f272d0e1999","tid":401064,"uid":31572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:39:10.000Z","msg":"有條件咪生囉<br />\n或者生一竇攞老綜都幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3633ab5a4d40fa58312ad8c003813952a250006","tid":401064,"uid":4209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"窮撚生仔正仆街"},{"pid":"cd56ea38095e27dcda880da11a74c77adab16688","tid":401064,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"仲要結婚，老婆會喺好多方面比壓力同限制你"},{"pid":"0c7bb0a85cf5dc46c747c92c03d998961b9bb195","tid":401064,"uid":117901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T04:41:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有條件咪生囉<br />\n或者生一竇攞老綜都幾爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj